title: Norwegian cruise ship coming to Port Canaveral
text: CAPE CANAVERAL, Fla. (AP) -- Norwegian Cruise Line's largest ship is going to call central Florida home. Norwegian officials on Monday said that Port Canaveral would be home to the Norwegian Epic, starting in November 2016. The ship will offer seven-day trips in the Caribbean, as well as three-day and four-day cruises to the Bahamas in 2017. The ship is the fifth-largest in the world.
